title: Body Count - Cop Killer (metalrap) 1992
description:
Body Count - Cop Killer (metalrap) 1992

This album is a reaction to the officers of L.A.P.D. who brutally beat up Rodney King during the LA Riots 1992. An album who says f**k you to police brutality, gang wars and rasism. Good, angry rapping with heavy guitars, an album that also shows that Ice-T is more a rocksinger than a rapper..
